  "prompt": "How does the legal system address complex money laundering schemes?",
  "response": "The legal system addresses money laundering through various strategies and legal mechanisms:\n\n1. Detection Methods\n- Financial transaction monitoring\n- Suspicious activity reporting\n- International cooperation between law enforcement agencies\n- Advanced technological tracking systems\n\n2. Legal Framework\n- Anti-Money Laundering (AML) regulations\n- Know Your Customer (KYC) compliance requirements\n- Criminal and civil asset forfeiture laws\n- International treaties and agreements\n\n3. Investigation Approaches\n- Forensic accounting techniques\n- Digital evidence analysis\n- Cross-border information sharing\n- Specialized investigative units\n\n4. Prosecution Strategies\n- Targeting financial intermediaries\n- Tracing complex transaction networks\n- Utilizing specialized financial crime prosecutors\n- Establishing paper trails\n\n5. Preventative Measures\n- Strict banking regulations\n- Mandatory reporting of large transactions\n- Background checks on financial institutions\n- Penalties for non-compliance\n\nThese approaches help combat sophisticated money laundering schemes through comprehensive legal and investigative strategies.",
